author: Written by: Sam Winstrom, Assignment Editor
title: Kenner Fire Department battling 3 alarm apartment blaze
text:
KENNER, LA (WVUE) - Firefighters are on the scene of an apartment fire in Kenner.
The fire broke out Sunday afternoon in the 4100 block of Alabama Avenue. Officials could not give specifics at the time, but said the fire is currently three-alarm fire.
Fox 8 is on the scene and will update this story as it develops.
